k的，好左9成<br />\n今年懶左用返洗頭水又有返，不過冇之前咁嚴重，等佢嚴重d先再試清水洗頭法"},{"pid":"5afe62ee3b1c53b241a1a5a27124f4bf3cdee2a8","tid":750084,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a7bb1d25b54d095518718d91489a9795b7eea1e","tid":750084,"uid":171426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f9a399037c4b6f5870c7be6eb327d77d5db5490","tid":750084,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"會唔會係脂溢性皮炎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:49:45.000Z","msg":"上年夏天又係咁，以為冬天好番就無事<br />\n點知一年一度又復發<br />\n睇過仁安專科，佢同我講係濕疹，開兩支類固純俾我，話真係頂唔順先用，仲唔可以超過3日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:37:16.000Z","msg":"試下用藥性洗頭水 IHERB買<br />\n<br />\n呢到好多討論 搵下就有"},{"pid":"164462e4456ab608b1b792d5b7e4af366082beb3","tid":750084,"uid":182701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/003118_16aa53923d986f7feb8e0ea80bf25c8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F003118_16aa53923d986f7feb8e0ea80bf25c8a.png&h=1a5d43a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前我都有<br />\n之後睇醫生 介紹呢隻 焦油黎<br />\n一排之後就冇事了<br />\n 用法係當佢好似平時洗頭水咁<br />\n搽晒成個頭<br />\n再等佢5-10分鐘先沖水<br />\n藥房應該有 萬寧好似都有得買<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}